fcft
------------------------------------------
fcft is a small font loading and glyph rasterization library built on-top of
FontConfig, FreeType2 and pixman.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.3-1
  libfcft-devel-3.1.5-1bl1
  libfcft4-3.1.5-1bl1
  libfontconfig-devel-2.13.1-2
  libfontconfig1-2.13.1-2
  libfreetype-devel-2.12.1-1
  libfreetype6-2.12.1-1
  libharfbuzz-devel-4.2.1-1
  libharfbuzz0-4.2.1-1
  libpixman1-devel-0.42.2-1
  libpixman1_0-0.42.2-1
  libutf8proc-devel-2.7.0-1bl1
  libutf8proc2-2.7.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.9.3-1
  tllist-1.0.5-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.39-1
  check-0.15.2-1
  cygport-0.35.5-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  libfontconfig-devel-2.13.1-2
  libfreetype-devel-2.12.1-1
  libharfbuzz-devel-4.2.1-1
  libpixman1-devel-0.42.2-1
  libutf8proc-devel-2.7.0-1bl1
  lua-5.3.6-4
  meson-0.63.3-1
  ninja-1.11.1-1
  scdoc-1.11.2-1bl2
  tllist-1.0.5-1bl1

Canonical website:
  https://codeberg.org/dnkl/fcft

Canonical download:
  https://codeberg.org/dnkl/fcft/archive/3.1.5.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack fcft-3.1.5-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./fcft-3.1.5-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/fcft-3.1.5-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/fcft-3.1.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfcft4-3.1.5-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfcft-devel-3.1.5-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

